    "en": {
      "title": "Attempt to seize Parliament: Tear gas attack",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In the wake of reports that attempts are being made to take over the Parliament, tight security arrangements have been made outside the Parliament.",
        "In this case, the police and soldiers who stopped the demonstrators who invaded the Parliament at the Poltua junction dispersed them by throwing teargas shells and splashing water on them."
      ],
